      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.G7p2YIGFTAU6uGjL]{Stellar Revelation}</p>\n<p><sub style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary);\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\" src=\"systems/sfrpg/images/cup/gameplay/photon.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></sub><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"> </span>Photon Revelation<br />You have learned how to use photonic power to bolster your allies in the face of danger. As a reaction while you&rsquo;re attuned or fully attuned, when an ally other than yourself within 30 feet of you takes damage, you can reduce the damage taken by your solarian level (minimum 0 damage). Once you use this revelation, you can&rsquo;t use it again until the next time you regain Stamina Points after a 10-minute rest.</p>"
